bs-pro-distribution-droplet-embed-desc: Botia makambo ya libanda uta na ba ebombelo ya Git, ndakisa. ba fichiers ya markdown
bs-pro-distribution-droplet-bitbucket-de: Botia fisyé uta na ebombelo ya BitBucket
bs-pro-distribution-droplets-ec-embed-la: Moko ya minoko oyo [https://prismjs.com/#supported-languges supported]. Esengeli kaka soki monoko ezwami te uta na bobakisi ya fisyé.
bs-pro-distribution-droplets-ec-embed-sh: Lakisa kaka milɔngɔ ya sikisiki. Ekoki kozala nimero ya molɔngɔ moko to esika oyo ekabwani na elembo (-). Mituya to ba intervalles ebele ya milɔngɔ ekoki kokabolama na virgule.
bs-pro-distribution-ec-config-file-white: Liste ya pembe ya extension ya fichier
Liste ya ba extensions ya fichier oyo epesami nzela. Tika pamba po ozala na restriction te.
bs-pro-distribution-ec-config-domain-whi: Liste ya ba domaines oyo epesami nzela ya ko intégrer contenus à partir ya. Kotia protocole te, kaka domaine. Ndakisa. `github.com`. Tika pamba po ozala na restriction te.
